Type: Package
Package: Gadest
Title: Global Analysis for Differential Expression of Single-cell
    Transcriptome
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Jianing", "Gao", , "gjn1106@mail.ustc.edu.cn", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6599-2133"))
Description: This package implements methods to: 1. Identify differential
    expressed genes (DEGs) of scRNA-seq data between two condition via
    linear mixed model; 2. Estimate the transcriptome shift across cell
    types; 3. Summerise the DEGs to gene modules.
